WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue {
font-size: 1em;
font-weight: bold;
color: #ffffff;
}

00:01:31.180 --> 00:01:34.700 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:01:34.820 --> 00:01:37.700 line:80%
=Episode 24=

00:01:53.930 --> 00:01:55.620 line:80%
Zigui is finally free.

00:01:56.540 --> 00:01:57.420 line:80%
All these years,

00:01:58.570 --> 00:01:59.900 line:80%
he was plagued by injuries,

00:02:01.370 --> 00:02:02.490 line:80%
homeless,

00:02:03.340 --> 00:02:04.700 line:80%
and hunted by his own sect.

00:02:06.730 --> 00:02:08.860 line:80%
He suffered too much.

00:02:09.300 --> 00:02:11.650 line:80%
It was no easy feat
for Uncle Guo to survive.

00:02:13.930 --> 00:02:16.340 line:80%
Why did Yin Dai insist on killing him?

00:02:17.300 --> 00:02:18.410 line:80%
Yin Dai claimed

00:02:20.140 --> 00:02:22.020 line:80%
Zigui signed a surrender letter

00:02:22.970 --> 00:02:24.210 line:80%
and disgraced the sect.

00:02:25.530 --> 00:02:26.370 line:80%
If you ask me,

00:02:27.060 --> 00:02:28.860 line:80%
he just didn't want Zigui to return.

00:02:29.520 --> 00:02:30.370 line:80%
Otherwise,

00:02:30.370 --> 00:02:31.490 line:80%
how could the Guos' estate

00:02:31.490 --> 00:02:33.780 line:80%
so rightfully fall
into Qingque Sect's hands?

00:02:35.370 --> 00:02:36.530 line:80%
The Yins' grand residence

00:02:37.180 --> 00:02:38.490 line:80%
and the Double Lotus Palace

00:02:39.090 --> 00:02:40.690 line:80%
were both built after that.

00:03:22.780 --> 00:03:24.620 line:80%
Yin Dai was after the Ziwei Method.

00:03:25.490 --> 00:03:27.816 line:80%
Using Nie Hengcheng's slaughter
of innocents as an excuse,

00:03:28.090 --> 00:03:29.210 line:80%
he incited the Six Sects

00:03:29.810 --> 00:03:30.780 line:80%
to attack Li Sect.

00:03:31.020 --> 00:03:32.020 line:80%
His true purpose

00:03:32.490 --> 00:03:33.490 line:80%
was to find out

00:03:33.490 --> 00:03:35.650 line:80%
why Nie Hengcheng's power
had grown so greatly.

00:03:38.180 --> 00:03:39.580 line:80%
He even sacrificed his disciples

00:03:39.970 --> 00:03:41.180 line:80%
to capture Elder Kaiyang,

00:03:41.610 --> 00:03:42.460 line:80%
and as he wished,

00:03:42.460 --> 00:03:44.090 line:80%
obtained the Ziwei Method.

00:03:44.650 --> 00:03:45.490 line:80%
From then on,

00:03:46.020 --> 00:03:47.553 line:80%
new and old grudges between both sides

00:03:47.740 --> 00:03:48.690 line:80%
ran deep,

00:03:49.410 --> 00:03:50.580 line:80%
like fire and water.

00:03:52.410 --> 00:03:54.370 line:80%
And he could begin his next move.

00:03:56.410 --> 00:03:57.370 line:80%
Stop.

00:04:00.860 --> 00:04:01.700 line:80%
Zhao,

00:04:03.180 --> 00:04:04.930 line:80%
do you know why your aunt

00:04:05.340 --> 00:04:06.780 line:80%
went alone to kill Nie Hengcheng?

00:04:07.300 --> 00:04:08.740 line:80%
Yin Dai knew his scheme

00:04:09.620 --> 00:04:11.530 line:80%
would one day be exposed by your aunt,

00:04:12.620 --> 00:04:14.126 line:80%
but he calculated one thing precisely,

00:04:14.530 --> 00:04:15.970 line:80%
and that was her character.

00:04:16.780 --> 00:04:18.340 line:80%
She could never stand by while Jianghu

00:04:18.340 --> 00:04:20.210 line:80%
was full of blood and corpses.

00:04:21.700 --> 00:04:22.610 line:80%
So, Yin Dai tricked her

00:04:22.610 --> 00:04:24.140 line:80%
into cultivating the Disintegration.

00:04:24.929 --> 00:04:26.925 line:80%
That way, he could kill
two birds with one stone.

00:04:26.970 --> 00:04:28.650 line:80%
- Shut up.
- He got rid

00:04:28.650 --> 00:04:30.940 line:80%
of Nie Hengcheng and your aunt.

00:04:35.700 --> 00:04:36.540 line:80%
That is the truth.

00:04:36.820 --> 00:04:37.660 line:80%
You can't hide

00:04:38.210 --> 00:04:39.050 line:80%
or escape it.

00:04:43.920 --> 00:04:45.233 line:80%
Blades are to be welded steadily,

00:04:45.580 --> 00:04:46.673 line:80%
but your heart is in chaos.

00:04:47.340 --> 00:04:48.320 line:80%
How can you wield it now?

00:04:49.410 --> 00:04:51.050 line:80%
You lost focus. Again.

00:04:59.170 --> 00:05:00.010 line:80%
Raise your hand.

00:05:00.340 --> 00:05:01.180 line:80%
Stand firm.

00:05:01.700 --> 00:05:02.540 line:80%
Continue.

00:05:17.850 --> 00:05:18.690 line:80%
Zhao,

00:05:19.940 --> 00:05:22.020 line:80%
martial arts are
to protect those beside you.

00:05:23.610 --> 00:05:24.700 line:80%
Though facing death,

00:05:25.210 --> 00:05:26.500 line:80%
it's for the sake of life.

00:05:27.210 --> 00:05:28.380 line:80%
Do you understand?

00:06:18.050 --> 00:06:19.380 line:80%
Aunt...

00:06:37.210 --> 00:06:39.900 line:80%
Give Zigui's ashes to your mother.

00:06:40.900 --> 00:06:42.420 line:80%
Ask her to take them back to Jiangdong

00:06:43.020 --> 00:06:44.860 line:80%
and scatter them
by the graves of his parents.

00:06:45.410 --> 00:06:46.970 line:80%
When you return to Luoying Valley,

00:06:47.210 --> 00:06:48.900 line:80%
light incense for your aunt
on my behalf.

00:06:49.850 --> 00:06:50.690 line:80%
Tell her

00:06:52.900 --> 00:06:54.780 line:80%
we live well here.

00:06:56.239 --> 00:06:58.192 line:80%
Our descendants
no longer practice martial arts.

00:06:58.290 --> 00:06:59.130 line:80%
From now on,

00:07:00.050 --> 00:07:01.090 line:80%
we have nothing more to do

00:07:02.530 --> 00:07:03.500 line:80%
with Jianghu.

00:07:04.460 --> 00:07:05.380 line:80%
It's a desolate place,

00:07:05.730 --> 00:07:06.820 line:80%
nothing worth much.

00:07:07.290 --> 00:07:09.020 line:80%
We brought you some food for the road.

00:07:10.700 --> 00:07:11.900 line:80%
This treasured sword...

00:07:12.700 --> 00:07:14.290 line:80%
A Qingque Sect disciple's blade.

00:07:14.650 --> 00:07:15.490 line:80%
That's right.

00:07:16.020 --> 00:07:17.580 line:80%
It was given to Zigui by Yin Dai

00:07:18.020 --> 00:07:19.246 line:80%
when he first entered the sect.

00:07:20.090 --> 00:07:22.210 line:80%
He once asked me to return it,

00:07:23.050 --> 00:07:24.850 line:80%
saying he disgraced the sect

00:07:25.210 --> 00:07:26.976 line:80%
and was unworthy
of being Master's disciple.

00:07:27.340 --> 00:07:28.180 line:80%
He considered it

00:07:28.650 --> 00:07:29.530 line:80%
as leaving the sect.

00:07:30.140 --> 00:07:30.980 line:80%
From then on,

00:07:31.500 --> 00:07:32.610 line:80%
he was no longer a disciple.

00:07:34.050 --> 00:07:34.890 line:80%
Zhao,

00:07:35.170 --> 00:07:36.650 line:80%
help deliver it as well.

00:07:50.530 --> 00:07:52.700 line:80%
Uncle Guo must've been heartbroken.

00:07:53.380 --> 00:07:54.580 line:80%
All these years,

00:07:54.580 --> 00:07:56.050 line:80%
has he had a single happy day?

00:07:57.850 --> 00:07:58.690 line:80%
That year,

00:07:59.050 --> 00:08:00.900 line:80%
when he heard Pingshu
killed Nie Hengcheng,

00:08:01.530 --> 00:08:02.700 line:80%
Zigui was still very pleased.

00:08:03.380 --> 00:08:05.170 line:80%
His heart for upholding justice

00:08:06.170 --> 00:08:07.730 line:80%
never completely turned cold.

00:08:09.090 --> 00:08:09.930 line:80%
Uncle Shi,

00:08:10.290 --> 00:08:12.020 line:80%
my mother once told me

00:08:12.340 --> 00:08:13.500 line:80%
that when Aunt traveled,

00:08:13.500 --> 00:08:15.506 line:80%
she befriended many friends
outside the Six Sects.

00:08:16.170 --> 00:08:17.900 line:80%
Was there anyone special among them?

00:08:18.210 --> 00:08:19.170 line:80%
Also,

00:08:19.170 --> 00:08:20.820 line:80%
when Aunt went alone to the duel,

00:08:21.460 --> 00:08:22.340 line:80%
where were they?

00:08:23.020 --> 00:08:23.993 line:80%
Why didn't they help her?

00:08:24.650 --> 00:08:27.170 line:80%
Back then, over half
of the Six Sects' elites perished.

00:08:27.170 --> 00:08:28.010 line:80%
As for the rest,

00:08:28.500 --> 00:08:30.780 line:80%
Yin Dai strictly ordered them not to go.

00:08:31.650 --> 00:08:33.980 line:80%
Those close to your aunt
and skilled in martial arts

00:08:34.290 --> 00:08:35.583 line:80%
were ambushed one after another.

00:08:35.860 --> 00:08:36.740 line:80%
Some died;

00:08:36.740 --> 00:08:37.580 line:80%
some were crippled.

00:08:38.740 --> 00:08:40.220 line:80%
Pingshu had no choice.

00:08:40.810 --> 00:08:42.050 line:80%
Was it Nie Hengcheng?

00:08:42.290 --> 00:08:43.450 line:80%
It could not have been him.

00:08:44.330 --> 00:08:46.330 line:80%
When Lu Chengnan stole
the Jade Sunflower,

00:08:46.620 --> 00:08:48.020 line:80%
Nie Hengcheng was greatly shaken,

00:08:48.410 --> 00:08:49.250 line:80%
nearly mad.

00:08:49.396 --> 00:08:51.789 line:80%
Fearing discovery by his followers
and the righteous sects,

00:08:51.860 --> 00:08:52.982 line:80%
he secluded himself to heal.

00:08:53.530 --> 00:08:55.410 line:80%
He had no time to set ambushes.

00:08:55.410 --> 00:08:56.860 line:80%
Mu is right.

00:08:57.220 --> 00:08:59.410 line:80%
Pingshu also believed
it wasn't Nie Hengcheng.

00:08:59.690 --> 00:09:01.140 line:80%
The culprit

00:09:01.900 --> 00:09:03.330 line:80%
remains unknown to this day.

00:09:04.500 --> 00:09:05.980 line:80%
It must've been the demonic sect.

00:09:07.050 --> 00:09:09.050 line:80%
We've left Jianghu behind,

00:09:09.690 --> 00:09:10.860 line:80%
but you are still within it.

00:09:11.780 --> 00:09:12.933 line:80%
Old causes are hard to end;

00:09:13.100 --> 00:09:14.320 line:80%
good outcomes are hard to reap.

00:09:14.450 --> 00:09:15.290 line:80%
The Six Sects

00:09:15.490 --> 00:09:17.220 line:80%
are deeply entangled
with the demonic sect.

00:09:17.220 --> 00:09:18.450 line:80%
You two young people

00:09:19.170 --> 00:09:20.450 line:80%
must take care of yourselves.

00:09:22.820 --> 00:09:25.580 line:80%
(Qinglong Altar)

00:09:25.650 --> 00:09:27.386 line:80%
Still playing with the peacock?

00:09:27.397 --> 00:09:29.290 line:80%
The Young Master has been out
for over a month.

00:09:29.290 --> 00:09:30.323 line:80%
Not going to look for him?

00:09:30.930 --> 00:09:33.290 line:80%
He's likely being lovey-dovey

00:09:33.690 --> 00:09:34.530 line:80%
with Miss Cai.

00:09:34.930 --> 00:09:36.076 line:80%
Why would we go disturb them?

00:09:36.170 --> 00:09:38.170 line:80%
Let him take his time.

00:09:38.570 --> 00:09:39.450 line:80%
No rush.

00:09:39.450 --> 00:09:41.610 line:80%
What if they truly elope?

00:09:44.330 --> 00:09:45.170 line:80%
Unlikely.

00:09:45.930 --> 00:09:46.980 line:80%
If they did,

00:09:48.380 --> 00:09:49.290 line:80%
not only our Li Sect,

00:09:50.000 --> 00:09:51.690 line:80%
but all the Six Sects would mobilize.

00:09:51.730 --> 00:09:53.569 line:80%
Besides, the Young Master
has grand ambitions.

00:09:53.620 --> 00:09:54.620 line:80%
To defy the world

00:09:54.810 --> 00:09:56.810 line:80%
and ruin his future for love

00:09:57.100 --> 00:09:59.050 line:80%
is not something he would do.

00:09:59.530 --> 00:10:00.370 line:80%
Future?

00:10:01.740 --> 00:10:03.650 line:80%
If Miss Cai likes it,

00:10:03.650 --> 00:10:06.650 line:80%
I think he'd pluck stars
and seize the moon.

00:10:06.650 --> 00:10:08.330 line:80%
A mere future and reputation

00:10:08.330 --> 00:10:10.140 line:80%
mean nothing to him.

00:10:12.860 --> 00:10:13.860 line:80%
Then I'll go look.

00:10:13.860 --> 00:10:14.700 line:80%
Hurry up.

00:10:16.480 --> 00:10:17.330 line:80%
What is it?

00:10:17.330 --> 00:10:18.336 line:80%
Hu Fengge was taken away.

00:10:18.810 --> 00:10:19.650 line:80%
What?

00:10:22.780 --> 00:10:23.706 line:80%
Another persimmon cake.

00:10:29.100 --> 00:10:30.386 line:80%
Still thinking about your aunt?

00:10:30.930 --> 00:10:31.980 line:80%
How could I not?

00:10:32.930 --> 00:10:34.570 line:80%
She knew Yin Dai's intentions

00:10:35.380 --> 00:10:37.450 line:80%
yet still chose to go alone.

00:10:38.860 --> 00:10:39.930 line:80%
No helpers,

00:10:41.070 --> 00:10:42.100 line:80%
no support.

00:10:43.140 --> 00:10:44.050 line:80%
She...

00:10:44.330 --> 00:10:46.050 line:80%
Nie Hengcheng and Yin Dai are dead.

00:10:46.810 --> 00:10:47.860 line:80%
Those who harmed your aunt

00:10:48.100 --> 00:10:48.980 line:80%
are gone.

00:10:49.620 --> 00:10:50.460 line:80%
No.

00:10:50.859 --> 00:10:52.345 line:80%
There is still the skin-painted demon

00:10:52.410 --> 00:10:53.380 line:80%
and the man in black.

00:11:02.100 --> 00:11:04.066 line:80%
Could the skin-painted demon
be the man in black?

00:11:04.810 --> 00:11:06.930 line:80%
He retrieved the saliva with my aunt

00:11:07.900 --> 00:11:09.620 line:80%
and knew about the Jade Sunflower.

00:11:09.620 --> 00:11:11.900 line:80%
He approached her with ulterior motives.

00:11:11.900 --> 00:11:13.450 line:80%
His scheming mind

00:11:13.450 --> 00:11:14.380 line:80%
and vast knowledge

00:11:14.810 --> 00:11:16.140 line:80%
are unfathomable.

00:11:17.620 --> 00:11:18.930 line:80%
But one thing is certain.

00:11:18.930 --> 00:11:20.170 line:80%
He is from your Li Sect.

00:11:20.690 --> 00:11:21.530 line:80%
There is

00:11:22.650 --> 00:11:25.020 line:80%
no record of such a person.

00:11:26.020 --> 00:11:27.860 line:80%
If the man in black is
the skin-painted demon,

00:11:28.140 --> 00:11:29.930 line:80%
he should've obtained
the Jade Sunflower.

00:11:29.930 --> 00:11:31.530 line:80%
Why slaughter the Chang clan?

00:11:32.860 --> 00:11:33.930 line:80%
Uncle Shi said

00:11:34.740 --> 00:11:35.842 line:80%
the mechanisms of Chang Fort

00:11:35.853 --> 00:11:37.293 line:80%
changed their core every three years.

00:11:37.810 --> 00:11:39.140 line:80%
Without someone guiding the way,

00:11:40.140 --> 00:11:40.980 line:80%
no one

00:11:41.740 --> 00:11:43.140 line:80%
could break in.

00:11:44.740 --> 00:11:46.450 line:80%
How did the man in black enter?

00:11:46.650 --> 00:11:47.490 line:80%
In recent years,

00:11:47.705 --> 00:11:49.358 line:80%
the only outsiders
who entered Chang Fort

00:11:49.410 --> 00:11:50.250 line:80%
were Ms. Luo

00:11:51.620 --> 00:11:52.810 line:80%
and me.

00:11:57.530 --> 00:12:00.860 line:80%
She was injured at Taichu Temple.

00:12:01.220 --> 00:12:03.380 line:80%
Why did she later appear at Chang Fort?

00:12:05.380 --> 00:12:06.410 line:80%
It was as if someone

00:12:07.020 --> 00:12:09.050 line:80%
deliberately let Uncle Chang see her.

00:12:09.980 --> 00:12:10.963 line:80%
As I once said,

00:12:10.974 --> 00:12:12.930 line:80%
among the killers
who slaughtered the Chang clan,

00:12:12.930 --> 00:12:14.140 line:80%
one emitted the Ethereal

00:12:14.140 --> 00:12:15.620 line:80%
of Taichu Temple.

00:12:15.620 --> 00:12:17.170 line:80%
I was certain it was Qiu Yuanfeng,

00:12:18.050 --> 00:12:19.740 line:80%
but I ignored Wang Yuanjing beside him.

00:12:20.930 --> 00:12:22.350 line:80%
But why would Wang Yuanjing do this?

00:12:25.570 --> 00:12:26.410 line:80%
Zhao,

00:12:27.100 --> 00:12:28.570 line:80%
didn't Uncle Shi say

00:12:28.930 --> 00:12:30.523 line:80%
Wang Yuanjing and Mr. Guo Zigui

00:12:30.534 --> 00:12:32.347 line:80%
were both imprisoned
in the EightClaw Prison?

00:12:33.330 --> 00:12:34.570 line:80%
Uncle Guo was captured,

00:12:35.410 --> 00:12:36.900 line:80%
yet Wang Yuanjing walked out.

00:12:37.410 --> 00:12:38.530 line:80%
At that time,

00:12:40.140 --> 00:12:42.050 line:80%
Mr. Wu was also imprisoned there.

00:12:42.930 --> 00:12:43.770 line:80%
You mean

00:12:44.100 --> 00:12:45.930 line:80%
Wang Yuanjing saw Wu Yuanying,

00:12:46.380 --> 00:12:47.650 line:80%
yet didn't rescue him?

00:12:49.450 --> 00:12:50.290 line:80%
Zhao,

00:12:51.410 --> 00:12:52.930 line:80%
did you find it strange

00:12:52.930 --> 00:12:54.570 line:80%
when Mr. Wu lunged

00:12:54.570 --> 00:12:56.620 line:80%
at Wang Yuanjing

00:12:56.620 --> 00:12:57.690 line:80%
at the memorial?

00:13:01.930 --> 00:13:02.770 line:80%
Yuanying!

00:13:05.050 --> 00:13:06.780 line:80%
Mr. Wu's expression

00:13:07.050 --> 00:13:08.780 line:80%
didn't look like joy at reunion,

00:13:11.330 --> 00:13:12.780 line:80%
but rather...

00:13:19.650 --> 00:13:20.570 line:80%
Hatred.

00:13:40.100 --> 00:13:40.940 line:80%
Zhao,

00:13:41.100 --> 00:13:42.410 line:80%
you're finally back.

00:13:42.410 --> 00:13:43.900 line:80%
We thought you were taken by Mu...

00:13:45.020 --> 00:13:45.860 line:80%
Well.

00:13:46.780 --> 00:13:49.500 line:80%
Mr. Mu took you for a stroll,

00:13:49.500 --> 00:13:51.140 line:80%
and you had too much fun to return.

00:13:51.530 --> 00:13:52.860 line:80%
- Chicken?
- Xingjia,

00:13:52.860 --> 00:13:53.780 line:80%
where are the others?

00:13:53.780 --> 00:13:54.930 line:80%
They are looking for you too.

00:13:55.500 --> 00:13:56.650 line:80%
Ever since you and Mr. Mu

00:13:57.170 --> 00:13:59.050 line:80%
went for that stroll,

00:13:59.050 --> 00:14:00.210 line:80%
this place has been in chaos.

00:14:01.020 --> 00:14:02.100 line:80%
What happened?

00:14:11.170 --> 00:14:13.100 line:80%
Someone leaked news

00:14:13.100 --> 00:14:15.140 line:80%
that you eloped with Mr. Mu.

00:14:15.140 --> 00:14:16.980 line:80%
Now, not only are your parents here,

00:14:16.980 --> 00:14:19.175 line:80%
but even Yang Heying,
Lord Yang, who thrives on chaos,

00:14:19.186 --> 00:14:20.620 line:80%
came to watch the show.

00:14:20.980 --> 00:14:22.740 line:80%
Master has a splitting headache.

00:14:22.740 --> 00:14:23.810 line:80%
Whoever leaked it

00:14:24.650 --> 00:14:25.740 line:80%
is a jerk!

00:14:26.100 --> 00:14:27.580 line:80%
Yes, a jerk!

00:14:30.210 --> 00:14:31.050 line:80%
Fan,

00:14:31.050 --> 00:14:33.050 line:80%
did Song Yuzhi truly cancel
the betrothal?

00:14:33.380 --> 00:14:34.220 line:80%
Absolutely.

00:14:35.220 --> 00:14:36.620 line:80%
He said to follow the natural cause,

00:14:37.140 --> 00:14:38.593 line:80%
but he couldn't hold back after all.

00:14:39.690 --> 00:14:40.530 line:80%
What do you mean?

00:14:41.570 --> 00:14:42.690 line:80%
Exactly what it sounds like.

00:14:47.290 --> 00:14:48.570 line:80%
You two,

00:14:49.210 --> 00:14:50.050 line:80%
what is going on?

00:14:50.050 --> 00:14:51.570 line:80%
What's going on?

00:14:52.220 --> 00:14:53.170 line:80%
Nothing is going on.

00:14:53.170 --> 00:14:54.010 line:80%
Back to business.

00:14:55.020 --> 00:14:56.900 line:80%
We think Taichu Temple is suspicious.

00:14:57.170 --> 00:14:58.410 line:80%
You've been staying here lately.

00:14:58.410 --> 00:14:59.523 line:80%
Have you seen Wang Yuanjing?

00:15:00.330 --> 00:15:01.290 line:80%
Not much.

00:15:01.930 --> 00:15:03.410 line:80%
All affairs in the temple

00:15:03.410 --> 00:15:05.020 line:80%
are handled by Mr. Li Min.

00:15:05.380 --> 00:15:06.930 line:80%
Lord Wang is rarely seen.

00:15:07.780 --> 00:15:08.810 line:80%
Fan,

00:15:08.810 --> 00:15:10.980 line:80%
what kind of person is Lord Wang?

00:15:12.140 --> 00:15:13.810 line:80%
The incident with Ms. Luo Yuanrong

00:15:13.810 --> 00:15:15.170 line:80%
hit him hard.

00:15:15.170 --> 00:15:17.930 line:80%
After all,
three fellow disciples died at once.

00:15:17.930 --> 00:15:20.140 line:80%
Who would not be upset?

00:15:21.220 --> 00:15:22.810 line:80%
After returning from Qingque Sect,

00:15:22.810 --> 00:15:24.410 line:80%
he immersed himself in alchemy

00:15:24.410 --> 00:15:25.290 line:80%
and cultivation,

00:15:25.290 --> 00:15:26.690 line:80%
claiming to have

00:15:26.690 --> 00:15:28.140 line:80%
seen through worldly matters

00:15:28.140 --> 00:15:29.570 line:80%
and seeking transcendence.

00:15:30.810 --> 00:15:31.650 line:80%
Transcendence?

00:15:32.740 --> 00:15:34.290 line:80%
He just fears vengeful spirits.

00:15:37.900 --> 00:15:38.810 line:80%
Zhao,

00:15:38.810 --> 00:15:40.290 line:80%
is there a problem with Lord Wang?

00:15:40.650 --> 00:15:41.490 line:80%
A big one.

00:15:41.860 --> 00:15:43.500 line:80%
But it's only a suspicion for now.

00:15:44.020 --> 00:15:44.930 line:80%
If we want proof,

00:15:44.930 --> 00:15:46.330 line:80%
he must admit it himself.

00:15:47.050 --> 00:15:48.930 line:80%
We need to get close to him

00:15:48.930 --> 00:15:50.570 line:80%
without arousing suspicion.

00:15:50.570 --> 00:15:52.290 line:80%
He rarely meets guests.

00:15:52.290 --> 00:15:54.290 line:80%
How can juniors like us approach him?

00:15:55.650 --> 00:15:56.683 line:80%
Isn't he afraid of death?

00:15:57.380 --> 00:15:58.410 line:80%
Then I think

00:15:58.410 --> 00:16:00.410 line:80%
he would be interested in an elixir

00:16:00.810 --> 00:16:01.650 line:80%
of immortality.

00:16:05.700 --> 00:16:09.940 line:80%
(Taichu Temple)

00:16:18.450 --> 00:16:20.930 line:80%
The Rebirth Pill?

00:16:21.410 --> 00:16:24.220 line:80%
Uncle Lei spent
over ten years refining it,

00:16:24.220 --> 00:16:26.650 line:80%
wasting countless herbs
to produce this single pill.

00:16:26.650 --> 00:16:29.140 line:80%
It's said that taking it

00:16:29.140 --> 00:16:31.290 line:80%
can free one from the three realms

00:16:31.290 --> 00:16:34.290 line:80%
and ascend to transformation
like Founder Beichen.

00:16:34.650 --> 00:16:36.290 line:80%
I was curious.

00:16:36.650 --> 00:16:39.860 line:80%
Lord Wang, I heard you study alchemy,

00:16:39.860 --> 00:16:41.020 line:80%
so I quietly

00:16:41.020 --> 00:16:42.860 line:80%
brought it for you to examine.

00:16:42.860 --> 00:16:44.100 line:80%
Is it truly that miraculous?

00:16:47.980 --> 00:16:49.500 line:80%
Indeed, good medicine.

00:16:55.380 --> 00:16:56.810 line:80%
Oh, my back...

00:17:00.410 --> 00:17:03.500 line:80%
Xiuming's medical skills have improved.

00:17:23.890 --> 00:17:24.890 line:80%
In two hours,

00:17:25.740 --> 00:17:26.740 line:80%
we can enter.

00:17:43.980 --> 00:17:45.090 line:80%
Yuanjing.

00:17:45.530 --> 00:17:46.780 line:80%
Yuanjing,

00:17:48.020 --> 00:17:49.940 line:80%
I can't die in peace.

00:17:49.940 --> 00:17:50.780 line:80%
Don't come closer.

00:17:52.130 --> 00:17:53.020 line:80%
Yuanjing.

00:17:54.050 --> 00:17:55.130 line:80%
Yuanjing,

00:17:56.330 --> 00:17:59.530 line:80%
when I sent a pigeon letter
to Taichu Temple,

00:17:59.530 --> 00:18:01.180 line:80%
why did you ignore my plea?

00:18:01.180 --> 00:18:02.290 line:80%
It didn't concern me.

00:18:02.290 --> 00:18:03.290 line:80%
Not me.

00:18:03.290 --> 00:18:06.290 line:80%
Did you hear the screams of my family?

00:18:06.290 --> 00:18:07.610 line:80%
It wasn't me, Chang.

00:18:07.610 --> 00:18:09.290 line:80%
- I'm innocent.
- My clan was killed.

00:18:09.290 --> 00:18:11.130 line:80%
I can't die in peace.

00:18:11.780 --> 00:18:12.660 line:80%
Yuanjing,

00:18:12.660 --> 00:18:14.330 line:80%
why didn't you save me?

00:18:14.330 --> 00:18:15.290 line:80%
Yuanying,

00:18:15.290 --> 00:18:17.290 line:80%
you died because of Qiu Yuanfeng.

00:18:17.290 --> 00:18:18.780 line:80%
He ignored you,

00:18:19.740 --> 00:18:20.610 line:80%
not me.

00:18:20.610 --> 00:18:24.370 line:80%
The EightClaw Prison.

00:18:37.220 --> 00:18:38.060 line:80%
Yuanying,

00:18:38.570 --> 00:18:39.850 line:80%
you're alive.

00:18:40.660 --> 00:18:41.740 line:80%
I'll rescue you now.

00:18:57.980 --> 00:18:59.220 line:80%
Yuanfeng said

00:18:59.810 --> 00:19:01.740 line:80%
you were killed by Elder Kaiyang.

00:19:04.290 --> 00:19:05.810 line:80%
Everyone thought you were dead.

00:19:06.980 --> 00:19:08.090 line:80%
Master is gone;

00:19:08.610 --> 00:19:09.850 line:80%
Uncle is invalid.

00:19:11.460 --> 00:19:14.130 line:80%
Yuanfeng's cultivation
is far inferior to mine.

00:19:16.810 --> 00:19:17.700 line:80%
They all said

00:19:20.290 --> 00:19:23.460 line:80%
I'd be the next lord of Taichu Temple.

00:19:24.780 --> 00:19:26.290 line:80%
As long as you were gone,

00:19:27.810 --> 00:19:31.370 line:80%
I could return home in glory as the lord

00:19:31.686 --> 00:19:32.943 line:80%
and bring honor to my ancestors.

00:19:34.610 --> 00:19:35.450 line:80%
Yuanying,

00:19:36.740 --> 00:19:38.290 line:80%
thanks for your help.

00:19:59.980 --> 00:20:02.180 line:80%
To conceal your filthy deeds,

00:20:02.530 --> 00:20:04.940 line:80%
you indirectly caused Guo Zigui's death.

00:20:05.220 --> 00:20:07.740 line:80%
Ironically, when you returned
to Taichu Temple,

00:20:07.740 --> 00:20:10.330 line:80%
you found Qiu Yuanfeng
inherited Uncle's cultivation

00:20:10.810 --> 00:20:12.420 line:80%
and beat you

00:20:12.420 --> 00:20:14.050 line:80%
during the sect competition.

00:20:14.420 --> 00:20:16.780 line:80%
The lord position never came to you.

00:20:17.050 --> 00:20:19.220 line:80%
That petty Qiu Yuanfeng

00:20:20.220 --> 00:20:24.020 line:80%
flattered Uncle endlessly
during recovery

00:20:24.020 --> 00:20:26.530 line:80%
and gained half his lifetime's power.

00:20:26.530 --> 00:20:28.370 line:80%
You went for wool and came home shorn,

00:20:28.370 --> 00:20:31.290 line:80%
leaving yourself vulnerable to others.

00:20:31.290 --> 00:20:33.940 line:80%
For that single thought,
you regretted it for over a decade,

00:20:33.940 --> 00:20:35.020 line:80%
yet you didn't repent

00:20:35.020 --> 00:20:37.090 line:80%
and caused over 100 deaths
in the Chang clan.

00:20:37.090 --> 00:20:37.940 line:80%
It wasn't me.

00:20:40.020 --> 00:20:41.780 line:80%
The demonic sect did it.

00:20:41.780 --> 00:20:43.980 line:80%
Who led them inside?

00:20:43.980 --> 00:20:45.570 line:80%
Who deceived Yuanrong?

00:20:45.570 --> 00:20:48.460 line:80%
Who opened Chang Fort's mechanisms

00:20:48.460 --> 00:20:50.290 line:80%
- and caused the massacre?
- It wasn't me.

00:20:52.020 --> 00:20:53.980 line:80%
I never meant to kill.

00:20:54.530 --> 00:20:55.810 line:80%
I did not.

00:20:56.130 --> 00:20:57.420 line:80%
Why didn't you save Yuanying?

00:20:57.420 --> 00:20:58.420 line:80%
Why didn't you save him?

00:20:58.420 --> 00:20:59.260 line:80%
Let go!

00:21:03.740 --> 00:21:05.180 line:80%
Expel her.

00:21:05.180 --> 00:21:06.020 line:80%
Yes.

00:21:10.050 --> 00:21:12.660 line:80%
If you don't want your mistake exposed,

00:21:12.660 --> 00:21:14.020 line:80%
do as I say.

00:21:19.300 --> 00:21:20.420 line:80%
(Chang Fort)
Who is there?

00:21:59.980 --> 00:22:01.370 line:80%
I never meant to kill them.

00:22:02.330 --> 00:22:03.610 line:80%
I did not.

00:22:03.610 --> 00:22:05.090 line:80%
He forced me.

00:22:06.290 --> 00:22:07.290 line:80%
If I didn't comply,

00:22:08.050 --> 00:22:10.660 line:80%
he'd tell everyone about my mistake.

00:22:11.290 --> 00:22:12.130 line:80%
Chang,

00:22:12.290 --> 00:22:14.570 line:80%
I only led them there.

00:22:18.660 --> 00:22:19.700 line:80%
Who is the man in black?

00:22:28.570 --> 00:22:29.410 line:80%
Who are you?

00:22:29.890 --> 00:22:31.130 line:80%
What poison did you give me?

00:22:32.180 --> 00:22:33.290 line:80%
Who am I?

00:22:34.850 --> 00:22:35.780 line:80%
I'm Chang Ning.

00:22:37.700 --> 00:22:38.540 line:80%
No.

00:22:39.220 --> 00:22:41.290 line:80%
You are Mu Qingyan,

00:22:41.850 --> 00:22:42.996 line:80%
who impersonated Chang Ning.

00:22:43.090 --> 00:22:43.930 line:80%
Guards!

00:22:44.740 --> 00:22:45.890 line:80%
Mr. Wu and Ms. Luo

00:22:45.890 --> 00:22:47.050 line:80%
treated you as family,

00:22:48.220 --> 00:22:50.050 line:80%
yet you caused their tragic deaths.

00:22:50.500 --> 00:22:52.020 line:80%
Mr. Chang treated you well,

00:22:53.276 --> 00:22:55.216 line:80%
yet you caused his entire can
to be slaughtered.

00:22:55.460 --> 00:22:57.420 line:80%
You deserve the most tragic end.

00:22:58.220 --> 00:22:59.060 line:80%
If he dies,

00:22:59.250 --> 00:23:00.890 line:80%
no one will know
who the man in black is.

00:23:07.090 --> 00:23:07.930 line:80%
Lord Wang.

00:23:12.740 --> 00:23:13.660 line:80%
The Chaos Needle.

00:23:13.980 --> 00:23:15.330 line:80%
You have it.

00:23:15.330 --> 00:23:17.020 line:80%
Better not act rashly again.

00:23:17.020 --> 00:23:17.860 line:80%
If you do,

00:23:18.500 --> 00:23:19.633 line:80%
I won't be able to stop him.

00:23:19.780 --> 00:23:22.050 line:80%
It seems you truly wish to die.

00:23:22.050 --> 00:23:22.930 line:80%
Very well.

00:23:22.940 --> 00:23:24.420 line:80%
I imagine the underworld

00:23:25.220 --> 00:23:28.020 line:80%
has many waiting to claim your life.

00:23:30.290 --> 00:23:31.130 line:80%
Cai Zhao,

00:23:31.610 --> 00:23:33.220 line:80%
as a disciple of the Six Sects,

00:23:33.220 --> 00:23:34.610 line:80%
you collude with a fiend.

00:23:35.130 --> 00:23:38.570 line:80%
Are you not afraid of shaming
your master and parents?

00:23:39.330 --> 00:23:40.220 line:80%
So what?

00:23:41.330 --> 00:23:42.610 line:80%
I'll simply tell the truth.

00:23:43.050 --> 00:23:44.420 line:80%
At worst, we gather everyone

00:23:44.420 --> 00:23:46.610 line:80%
and lay out your ugly deeds

00:23:46.610 --> 00:23:48.180 line:80%
one by one.

00:23:48.180 --> 00:23:49.940 line:80%
You left Mr. Wu in that prison,

00:23:49.940 --> 00:23:51.890 line:80%
set a trap for Ms. Luo,

00:23:51.890 --> 00:23:53.290 line:80%
and caused Uncle Chang's death.

00:23:53.290 --> 00:23:54.130 line:80%
Nonsense.

00:23:54.530 --> 00:23:55.460 line:80%
No one will believe you.

00:23:55.850 --> 00:23:56.690 line:80%
Lord Wang,

00:23:57.090 --> 00:23:59.130 line:80%
I refuse to believe no one saw you

00:24:00.020 --> 00:24:01.420 line:80%
take Ms. Luo to Chang Fort.

00:24:02.420 --> 00:24:04.090 line:80%
If we investigate carefully,

00:24:04.090 --> 00:24:05.330 line:80%
we will find witnesses.

00:24:06.050 --> 00:24:07.500 line:80%
Would you like to try?

00:24:09.700 --> 00:24:10.570 line:80%
Wang Yuanjing,

00:24:10.570 --> 00:24:12.330 line:80%
if you tell me the name
of the man in black,

00:24:12.940 --> 00:24:14.290 line:80%
I can spare your life.

00:24:14.290 --> 00:24:15.740 line:80%
You may continue as the Lord.

00:24:16.420 --> 00:24:18.810 line:80%
I won't mention the past.

00:24:18.810 --> 00:24:20.810 line:80%
We go our separate ways.

00:24:20.810 --> 00:24:22.530 line:80%
Why would you spare me?

00:24:23.740 --> 00:24:25.810 line:80%
The one who slaughtered the Chang clan

00:24:26.980 --> 00:24:28.570 line:80%
wasn't you, but that man in black.

00:24:28.850 --> 00:24:31.020 line:80%
I only want to find him and kill him

00:24:31.330 --> 00:24:32.890 line:80%
to avenge the Chang clan.

00:24:32.890 --> 00:24:34.370 line:80%
As for Mr. Wu

00:24:34.370 --> 00:24:35.330 line:80%
and Guo Zigui,

00:24:36.610 --> 00:24:38.160 line:80%
I have no interest

00:24:38.171 --> 00:24:39.493 line:80%
in your Six Sects' petty schemes.

00:24:40.000 --> 00:24:40.850 line:80%
Think about it.

00:24:40.850 --> 00:24:42.530 line:80%
If that person dies,

00:24:42.530 --> 00:24:44.660 line:80%
you lose someone
holding leverage over you.

00:24:45.020 --> 00:24:46.460 line:80%
Isn't that perfect?

00:24:46.810 --> 00:24:48.500 line:80%
As long as you tell us his name,

00:24:49.130 --> 00:24:49.970 line:80%
I guarantee

00:24:51.420 --> 00:24:52.330 line:80%
he won't kill you.

00:24:55.660 --> 00:24:56.500 line:80%
Fine.

00:24:58.090 --> 00:24:58.930 line:80%
I'll tell you.

00:25:00.050 --> 00:25:01.740 line:80%
Though he covered his face,

00:25:03.020 --> 00:25:05.420 line:80%
I recognized his eyes.

00:25:07.420 --> 00:25:08.460 line:80%
He is...

00:25:14.740 --> 00:25:15.580 line:80%
He is outside.

00:25:16.660 --> 00:25:19.130 line:80%
Seize the assassin!

00:25:28.700 --> 00:25:29.850 line:80%
- Watch them.
- Yes.

00:25:32.530 --> 00:25:33.370 line:80%
Lord Wang!

00:25:34.740 --> 00:25:36.290 line:80%
They killed Lord Wang.

00:25:36.290 --> 00:25:37.130 line:80%
Wait.

00:25:39.370 --> 00:25:40.290 line:80%
We didn't kill him.

00:25:41.660 --> 00:25:42.500 line:80%
Mu Qingyan,

00:25:42.700 --> 00:25:44.660 line:80%
Chief of the demonic sect.

00:25:45.290 --> 00:25:46.180 line:80%
You know me?

00:25:46.500 --> 00:25:48.940 line:80%
I saw you in Qingque Town.

00:25:49.610 --> 00:25:50.450 line:80%
Cai Zhao,

00:25:50.700 --> 00:25:51.940 line:80%
as a disciple of the Six Sects,

00:25:52.460 --> 00:25:53.773 line:80%
why collude with the demonic sect

00:25:53.784 --> 00:25:54.810 line:80%
and murder our lord?

00:25:54.810 --> 00:25:57.420 line:80%
What right does she have
to collude with me?

00:25:59.050 --> 00:26:00.130 line:80%
She's merely

00:26:02.290 --> 00:26:04.050 line:80%
a hostage I seized.

00:26:04.890 --> 00:26:06.090 line:80%
Do you think I'd believe that?

00:26:06.570 --> 00:26:07.410 line:80%
Cai Zhao,

00:26:08.290 --> 00:26:10.020 line:80%
don't think you can clear yourself.

00:26:10.420 --> 00:26:11.370 line:80%
Speak.

00:26:11.370 --> 00:26:12.980 line:80%
Why did you kill our lord?

00:26:12.980 --> 00:26:14.130 line:80%
He was scum.

00:26:15.130 --> 00:26:16.500 line:80%
I killed him.

00:26:16.850 --> 00:26:18.330 line:80%
What can you do?

00:26:18.330 --> 00:26:19.530 line:80%
Outrageous.

00:26:19.530 --> 00:26:20.460 line:80%
I'll kill you.

00:26:24.290 --> 00:26:25.130 line:80%
You can touch me,

00:26:26.050 --> 00:26:27.070 line:80%
but why touch my hostage?

00:26:27.460 --> 00:26:28.500 line:80%
What are you waiting for?

00:26:28.500 --> 00:26:29.660 line:80%
Avenge Lord Wang!

00:26:29.660 --> 00:26:31.020 line:80%
Stop! Stop!

00:26:31.570 --> 00:26:32.530 line:80%
Zhao!

00:26:32.850 --> 00:26:33.690 line:80%
My father is here.

00:26:34.130 --> 00:26:34.980 line:80%
I'll be fine.

00:26:34.980 --> 00:26:35.820 line:80%
Go first.

00:26:38.020 --> 00:26:39.460 line:80%
(Alchemy Room)

00:26:41.460 --> 00:26:42.300 line:80%
Father.

00:26:43.780 --> 00:26:44.620 line:80%
Mother.

00:26:53.740 --> 00:26:56.860 line:80%
(Nie Zhe contacted a mole
and rescued Hu Fengge.)

00:27:01.860 --> 00:27:04.340 line:80%
(Taichu Temple)

00:27:06.940 --> 00:27:08.890 line:80%
I knew he wasn't dead.

00:27:10.850 --> 00:27:11.850 line:80%
Zigui

00:27:12.530 --> 00:27:13.576 line:80%
had always been like that.

00:27:14.610 --> 00:27:16.370 line:80%
If he made a mistake,

00:27:16.370 --> 00:27:17.890 line:80%
he'd hide somewhere outside.

00:27:18.740 --> 00:27:20.780 line:80%
I kept waiting for him to come back.

00:27:20.780 --> 00:27:22.090 line:80%
I thought

00:27:22.090 --> 00:27:23.530 line:80%
even if he didn't show himself,

00:27:24.940 --> 00:27:26.700 line:80%
he must be living well

00:27:28.220 --> 00:27:29.940 line:80%
in some remote mountains.

00:27:30.530 --> 00:27:31.610 line:80%
Who knew...

00:27:33.180 --> 00:27:34.130 line:80%
Stop crying.

00:27:34.700 --> 00:27:36.940 line:80%
Zhao said he passed peacefully.

00:27:36.940 --> 00:27:38.780 line:80%
He settled what needed settling.

00:27:38.780 --> 00:27:40.370 line:80%
Isn't that all life amounts to?

00:27:40.370 --> 00:27:41.330 line:80%
That is enough.

00:27:41.330 --> 00:27:42.780 line:80%
Are you even human?

00:27:42.780 --> 00:27:43.876 line:80%
Didn't you hear Zhao say

00:27:43.887 --> 00:27:45.220 line:80%
he was tortured beyond recognition

00:27:45.220 --> 00:27:46.570 line:80%
by Nie Hengcheng's men

00:27:47.220 --> 00:27:49.740 line:80%
and suffered for over a decade
on his sickbed?

00:27:50.940 --> 00:27:52.090 line:80%
You call that peaceful?

00:27:52.930 --> 00:27:53.660 line:80%
Enough.

00:27:53.671 --> 00:27:55.500 line:80%
A traitor who surrendered
to the demonic sect

00:27:55.500 --> 00:27:57.255 line:80%
managed to live
for over a decade in hiding.

00:27:57.266 --> 00:27:58.370 line:80%
That was already fortune.

00:27:58.370 --> 00:27:59.444 line:80%
Had he dared show himself,

00:27:59.850 --> 00:28:02.290 line:80%
Lord Yin would've punished him
by the rules.

00:28:02.290 --> 00:28:03.460 line:80%
Enough chatter.

00:28:06.090 --> 00:28:08.130 line:80%
I know a little
about the Piercing Strike

00:28:08.660 --> 00:28:09.740 line:80%
of the demonic sect,

00:28:09.740 --> 00:28:11.530 line:80%
but I'm having a hard time mastering it.

00:28:11.530 --> 00:28:13.290 line:80%
What luck running into you today.

00:28:13.290 --> 00:28:14.570 line:80%
Come. Spar with me.

00:28:14.570 --> 00:28:15.780 line:80%
Cai Pingchun, are you crazy?

00:28:15.780 --> 00:28:17.180 line:80%
You crossed the line first.

00:28:17.180 --> 00:28:18.530 line:80%
Let's see if this strike

00:28:18.530 --> 00:28:19.850 line:80%
can hurt you.

00:28:19.850 --> 00:28:20.940 line:80%
Then do it. Why waste words?

00:28:20.940 --> 00:28:22.330 line:80%
- Come on.
- Stop!

00:28:26.810 --> 00:28:29.550 line:80%
Yuanjing's body still lies here,

00:28:30.500 --> 00:28:32.180 line:80%
yet as elders,

00:28:32.180 --> 00:28:33.610 line:80%
you bicker before the juniors.

00:28:34.570 --> 00:28:36.050 line:80%
Stop embarrassing yourselves.

00:28:36.050 --> 00:28:37.420 line:80%
Thank you, Lord Qi,

00:28:37.420 --> 00:28:38.980 line:80%
for remembering our slain lord.

00:28:38.980 --> 00:28:39.890 line:80%
I'm incompetent.

00:28:40.890 --> 00:28:43.020 line:80%
Lord Qi, please uphold justice
for Lord Wang

00:28:43.780 --> 00:28:45.090 line:80%
and punish the true culprit

00:28:45.090 --> 00:28:47.460 line:80%
to give all Taichu Temple disciples
an explanation.

00:28:50.610 --> 00:28:51.463 line:80%
Master,

00:28:51.474 --> 00:28:53.187 line:80%
you need not fear
Taichu Temple's trouble.

00:28:53.370 --> 00:28:54.290 line:80%
I did nothing wrong.

00:28:55.220 --> 00:28:56.060 line:80%
Wang Yuanjing

00:28:56.290 --> 00:28:57.180 line:80%
deserved death.

00:28:57.500 --> 00:28:58.340 line:80%
Zhao,

00:28:58.610 --> 00:28:59.500 line:80%
stop.

00:28:59.500 --> 00:29:01.060 line:80%
Li, don't worry.

00:29:01.530 --> 00:29:04.220 line:80%
I know you shared deep ties
with your lord.

00:29:04.810 --> 00:29:07.610 line:80%
But dismissing the other disciples

00:29:07.610 --> 00:29:08.850 line:80%
and keeping matters quiet

00:29:09.220 --> 00:29:10.610 line:80%
is also for your lord's sake.

00:29:10.610 --> 00:29:12.420 line:80%
Lord Song, what do you mean?

00:29:12.420 --> 00:29:14.570 line:80%
Didn't you hear Zhao?

00:29:15.130 --> 00:29:17.420 line:80%
If Lord Wang truly left Mr. Wu
in that prison...

00:29:17.420 --> 00:29:18.780 line:80%
That's slander

00:29:19.420 --> 00:29:21.700 line:80%
from that demonic fiend.

00:29:21.700 --> 00:29:22.850 line:80%
Who'd believe it?

00:29:23.330 --> 00:29:24.530 line:80%
As everyone knows,

00:29:24.541 --> 00:29:26.636 line:80%
Uncle Wang was always kind,
gentle, and magnanimous.

00:29:28.130 --> 00:29:28.970 line:80%
Cai Zhao,

00:29:29.810 --> 00:29:32.660 line:80%
you must've colluded
with Mu Qingyan to kill him.

00:29:33.090 --> 00:29:33.930 line:80%
Li,

00:29:34.780 --> 00:29:36.530 line:80%
we examined Lord Wang's sword wound.

00:29:37.050 --> 00:29:39.610 line:80%
The swordsman possessed
immense inner force,

00:29:39.610 --> 00:29:41.090 line:80%
beyond Zhao's ability.

00:29:41.570 --> 00:29:43.530 line:80%
Even Mu Qingyan
may not have such cultivation.

00:29:46.500 --> 00:29:47.846 line:80%
The demonic sect has many masters.

00:29:48.610 --> 00:29:49.500 line:80%
Who knows

00:29:49.500 --> 00:29:50.980 line:80%
if it was someone else?

00:29:51.500 --> 00:29:52.340 line:80%
Cai Zhao,

00:29:53.370 --> 00:29:54.740 line:80%
killing was bad enough,

00:29:55.610 --> 00:29:57.370 line:80%
yet you smear Lord Wang's name.

00:29:57.370 --> 00:29:58.850 line:80%
What is your intent?

00:29:59.330 --> 00:30:00.420 line:80%
I do have intent.

00:30:02.370 --> 00:30:03.460 line:80%
Everyone, do you remember

00:30:04.220 --> 00:30:06.180 line:80%
that at Founder Beichen's memorial,

00:30:06.570 --> 00:30:07.410 line:80%
how Mr. Wu reacted

00:30:07.850 --> 00:30:10.370 line:80%
when Lord Wang approached Mr. Wu,

00:30:11.020 --> 00:30:12.740 line:80%
whose meridians were severed?

00:30:12.740 --> 00:30:13.580 line:80%
I remember.

00:30:13.780 --> 00:30:15.610 line:80%
He could not see,

00:30:15.610 --> 00:30:18.050 line:80%
but upon hearing Lord Wang's voice,
he raised his head,

00:30:18.050 --> 00:30:20.530 line:80%
identified the direction, and lunged.

00:30:21.610 --> 00:30:23.020 line:80%
He seemed extremely agitated.

00:30:27.180 --> 00:30:28.050 line:80%
Zhao,

00:30:28.050 --> 00:30:29.220 line:80%
you mean

00:30:29.690 --> 00:30:30.570 line:80%
he wasn't falling

00:30:30.570 --> 00:30:32.290 line:80%
into Wang Yuanjing's arms?

00:30:32.720 --> 00:30:33.610 line:80%
He wanted...

00:30:33.610 --> 00:30:35.220 line:80%
He wanted to bite Wang's throat.

00:30:37.050 --> 00:30:38.420 line:80%
That does seem so.

00:30:39.290 --> 00:30:42.330 line:80%
If Mr. Wu tried
to bite him before dying,

00:30:42.330 --> 00:30:43.460 line:80%
Wang Yuanjing

00:30:43.460 --> 00:30:45.130 line:80%
must have wronged him.

00:30:45.570 --> 00:30:47.740 line:80%
When Wang Yuanjing entered
the EightClaw Prison,

00:30:49.290 --> 00:30:51.050 line:80%
Wu was alive and well.

00:30:51.890 --> 00:30:53.530 line:80%
Had he been saved then,

00:30:53.980 --> 00:30:56.130 line:80%
he wouldn't have suffered later.

00:30:56.530 --> 00:30:57.370 line:80%
Yeah.

00:30:57.780 --> 00:30:58.620 line:80%
How tragic.

00:30:59.420 --> 00:31:00.660 line:80%
With a few words,

00:31:01.530 --> 00:31:03.420 line:80%
you condemn Lord Wang?

00:31:04.050 --> 00:31:04.890 line:80%
So now,

00:31:05.570 --> 00:31:08.130 line:80%
Mu Qingyan is righteous,

00:31:08.130 --> 00:31:10.460 line:80%
and Lord Wang is evil?

00:31:10.460 --> 00:31:11.300 line:80%
You

00:31:11.980 --> 00:31:13.220 line:80%
simply bully Taichu Temple

00:31:13.220 --> 00:31:14.220 line:80%
in its decline.

00:31:14.780 --> 00:31:15.660 line:80%
Li,

00:31:15.660 --> 00:31:16.850 line:80%
the Six Sects are as one.

00:31:17.290 --> 00:31:19.700 line:80%
There is no bullying.

00:31:20.570 --> 00:31:23.570 line:80%
If Lord Wang truly committed
such disgrace,

00:31:24.180 --> 00:31:26.940 line:80%
the Six Sects would not shield him.

00:31:27.700 --> 00:31:28.540 line:80%
Fine.

00:31:29.420 --> 00:31:31.180 line:80%
Even if he failed to save someone,

00:31:33.700 --> 00:31:35.370 line:80%
it wasn't a capital crime.

00:31:35.700 --> 00:31:36.780 line:80%
Let me ask you.

00:31:38.420 --> 00:31:39.850 line:80%
If he conspired with the man in black

00:31:40.700 --> 00:31:43.180 line:80%
and caused over 100 deaths
in the Chang clan,

00:31:43.780 --> 00:31:44.810 line:80%
does he deserve death?

00:31:44.810 --> 00:31:45.929 line:80%
Enough of this man in black.

00:31:46.660 --> 00:31:48.980 line:80%
A grand-master in black?

00:31:48.980 --> 00:31:50.610 line:80%
You made him up.

00:31:50.610 --> 00:31:52.180 line:80%
It's your conspiracy.

00:31:53.180 --> 00:31:54.020 line:80%
Li,

00:31:54.700 --> 00:31:56.500 line:80%
to know the truth,

00:31:56.500 --> 00:31:59.370 line:80%
we need only find Mu Qingyan.

00:32:00.180 --> 00:32:01.370 line:80%
For now,

00:32:01.980 --> 00:32:04.050 line:80%
let Lord Wang be laid to rest.

00:32:04.980 --> 00:32:05.820 line:80%
All matters

00:32:06.220 --> 00:32:08.330 line:80%
will be discussed after the funeral.

00:32:09.660 --> 00:32:11.060 line:80%
Yuzhi, Zhao,

00:32:11.890 --> 00:32:12.730 line:80%
come with me.

00:32:23.810 --> 00:32:24.650 line:80%
Stop.

00:32:26.050 --> 00:32:27.610 line:80%
Taichu Temple

00:32:27.610 --> 00:32:29.570 line:80%
won't let Cai Zhao leave!
She's the murderer!

00:32:38.220 --> 00:32:39.850 line:80%
You shield your own.

00:32:40.330 --> 00:32:42.199 line:80%
Whether she colluded with Mu Qingyan

00:32:42.210 --> 00:32:43.980 line:80%
and killed Lord Wang
requires investigation.

00:32:43.980 --> 00:32:45.500 line:80%
She can't leave.

00:32:45.500 --> 00:32:47.050 line:80%
Of course, it will be investigated.

00:32:48.370 --> 00:32:50.420 line:80%
But Zhao can't stay here.

00:32:50.740 --> 00:32:52.890 line:80%
If she doesn't stay here,
what if she runs?

00:32:53.220 --> 00:32:54.060 line:80%
Lady Ning,

00:32:54.740 --> 00:32:57.570 line:80%
she's disappeared before, right?

00:32:59.500 --> 00:33:00.810 line:80%
Zhao is my disciple.

00:33:01.180 --> 00:33:02.460 line:80%
I guarantee for her.

00:33:02.850 --> 00:33:04.700 line:80%
Until the matter is clear,

00:33:04.980 --> 00:33:06.940 line:80%
she won't leave Qingque Sect.

00:33:07.460 --> 00:33:08.500 line:80%
Li, refrain

00:33:09.290 --> 00:33:10.570 line:80%
from reckless words.

00:33:15.290 --> 00:33:16.130 line:80%
Taichu Temple

00:33:17.050 --> 00:33:18.180 line:80%
is still among the Six Sects.

00:33:18.740 --> 00:33:20.180 line:80%
As head of the Six Sects,

00:33:20.810 --> 00:33:22.050 line:80%
I'm not decoration.

00:33:31.090 --> 00:33:32.090 line:80%
Mind yourself.

00:33:32.660 --> 00:33:33.500 line:80%
Let's go.

00:33:45.940 --> 00:33:47.940 line:80%
I've warned you repeatedly

00:33:47.940 --> 00:33:49.940 line:80%
that Mu Qingyan is no good man,

00:33:49.940 --> 00:33:51.090 line:80%
but you refused to listen.

00:33:51.700 --> 00:33:53.180 line:80%
You were deceived by him

00:33:53.180 --> 00:33:54.890 line:80%
and ended up like this.

00:33:54.890 --> 00:33:56.850 line:80%
Do you know how the Six Sects' disciples

00:33:56.850 --> 00:33:58.890 line:80%
speak of you in private?

00:33:59.980 --> 00:34:00.820 line:80%
Master,

00:34:01.980 --> 00:34:03.660 line:80%
I left alone

00:34:03.660 --> 00:34:05.570 line:80%
to seek the Shi brothers

00:34:05.570 --> 00:34:06.980 line:80%
for news of the Jade Sunflower

00:34:07.610 --> 00:34:08.580 line:80%
to heal Yuzhi.

00:34:08.890 --> 00:34:10.060 line:80%
Traveling with Mu Qingyan

00:34:10.970 --> 00:34:13.290 line:80%
was to investigate
the skin-painted demon.

00:34:13.580 --> 00:34:14.420 line:80%
Also,

00:34:15.180 --> 00:34:17.490 line:80%
the killer in the hall
was not Mu Qingyan.

00:34:17.490 --> 00:34:18.450 line:80%
It was the man in black.

00:34:18.450 --> 00:34:19.540 line:80%
I saw him myself.

00:34:19.540 --> 00:34:21.270 line:80%
Did Mu Qingyan also say

00:34:21.281 --> 00:34:23.060 line:80%
that the man in black
is from our Six Sects?

00:34:23.810 --> 00:34:24.970 line:80%
Have you considered

00:34:24.970 --> 00:34:27.850 line:80%
that everything you saw
may have been an illusion,

00:34:27.850 --> 00:34:30.140 line:80%
arranged by Mu Qingyan?

00:34:31.700 --> 00:34:34.010 line:80%
With a nonexistent man in black,

00:34:34.010 --> 00:34:36.580 line:80%
he sows distrust among the Six Sects.

00:34:36.580 --> 00:34:37.930 line:80%
This is

00:34:37.930 --> 00:34:39.850 line:80%
a brilliant move indeed.

00:34:40.330 --> 00:34:41.850 line:80%
I'll say it once more.

00:34:42.740 --> 00:34:43.780 line:80%
The skin-painted demon

00:34:45.100 --> 00:34:46.810 line:80%
can never be trusted.

00:34:53.810 --> 00:34:54.930 line:80%
I heard Luoying Valley

00:34:54.930 --> 00:34:55.890 line:80%
produces demonesses.

00:34:56.330 --> 00:34:58.780 line:80%
This one is like her ancestor,

00:34:59.220 --> 00:35:01.140 line:80%
colluding with the demonic sect chief

00:35:01.140 --> 00:35:02.446 line:80%
and killing Taichu Temple's lord.

00:35:03.220 --> 00:35:04.290 line:80%
Such scum.

00:35:04.290 --> 00:35:06.010 line:80%
Yet Lord Qi still protects her.

00:35:06.810 --> 00:35:08.450 line:80%
She colluded with the demonic sect

00:35:08.450 --> 00:35:10.290 line:80%
and betrayed her sect.

00:35:10.290 --> 00:35:11.660 line:80%
She should be executed

00:35:11.660 --> 00:35:12.500 line:80%
to set an example.

00:35:14.580 --> 00:35:15.660 line:80%
Who are you

00:35:15.660 --> 00:35:16.860 line:80%
to slander Qingque Sect?

00:35:17.970 --> 00:35:18.810 line:80%
This girl...

00:35:19.930 --> 00:35:20.850 line:80%
She has a quick temper.

00:35:21.290 --> 00:35:22.410 line:80%
Please forgive her.

00:35:22.410 --> 00:35:24.060 line:80%
The demoness rumor is false.

00:35:24.620 --> 00:35:25.850 line:80%
Spreading rumors is unwise.

00:35:28.700 --> 00:35:29.850 line:80%
He is Song Yuzhi,

00:35:29.850 --> 00:35:31.100 line:80%
Lord Qi's third disciple.

00:35:31.100 --> 00:35:31.940 line:80%
What are you doing?

00:35:34.740 --> 00:35:35.580 line:80%
Mr. Song,

00:35:35.850 --> 00:35:36.850 line:80%
we meant no offense.

00:35:37.620 --> 00:35:38.460 line:80%
Waiter.

00:35:38.480 --> 00:35:39.780 line:80%
This table is on me.

00:35:39.810 --> 00:35:40.710 line:80%
Sure.

00:35:40.710 --> 00:35:43.100 line:80%
These gossipers

00:35:43.100 --> 00:35:44.540 line:80%
deserve a lesson.

00:35:44.540 --> 00:35:46.700 line:80%
That's just nonsense.

00:35:46.700 --> 00:35:48.100 line:80%
- Ignore them.
- Exactly.

00:35:48.580 --> 00:35:49.920 line:80%
Zhao hardly looks like a demoness.

00:35:52.290 --> 00:35:53.220 line:80%
Cai Zhao,

00:35:53.220 --> 00:35:54.810 line:80%
did you collude with Mu Qingyan?

00:35:54.810 --> 00:35:56.970 line:80%
- Lingbo.
- You still defend her?

00:35:56.970 --> 00:35:59.100 line:80%
Listen to what they say about us.

00:36:00.890 --> 00:36:01.706 line:80%
Cai Zhao,

00:36:01.717 --> 00:36:03.466 line:80%
if you truly colluded
with the demonic sect

00:36:03.477 --> 00:36:04.720 line:80%
and shamed Father and the sect,

00:36:04.731 --> 00:36:06.290 line:80%
I'll be the first to spare you no mercy.

00:36:06.290 --> 00:36:07.220 line:80%
Lingbo,

00:36:07.220 --> 00:36:08.320 line:80%
I didn't kill Wang Yuanjing.

00:36:09.180 --> 00:36:10.820 line:80%
What's your relationship
with Mu Qingyan?

00:36:10.970 --> 00:36:12.850 line:80%
Where did you go these past weeks?

00:36:15.620 --> 00:36:16.460 line:80%
Master.

00:36:17.450 --> 00:36:18.290 line:80%
Father.

00:36:18.450 --> 00:36:19.580 line:80%
This is a critical time.

00:36:20.010 --> 00:36:20.970 line:80%
As fellow disciples,

00:36:22.010 --> 00:36:23.580 line:80%
you should stand together

00:36:23.580 --> 00:36:24.540 line:80%
against a common foe.

00:36:24.540 --> 00:36:26.220 line:80%
Yet look at yourselves.

00:36:28.100 --> 00:36:28.940 line:80%
This entire matter

00:36:29.540 --> 00:36:30.850 line:80%
began with Mu Qingyan.

00:36:31.140 --> 00:36:31.980 line:80%
Your Uncle Li

00:36:32.290 --> 00:36:33.740 line:80%
is pursuing him

00:36:34.370 --> 00:36:35.660 line:80%
to give Taichu Temple justice.

00:36:36.100 --> 00:36:37.220 line:80%
Until this is resolved,

00:36:37.660 --> 00:36:38.740 line:80%
no one

00:36:39.450 --> 00:36:40.810 line:80%
is to speak ill of Zhao.

00:36:41.020 --> 00:36:41.930 line:80%
- Yes.
- Yes.

00:36:41.930 --> 00:36:42.780 line:80%
Yes, Master.

00:36:44.010 --> 00:36:45.010 line:80%
Especially you.

00:37:03.180 --> 00:37:04.020 line:80%
Mother.

00:37:05.290 --> 00:37:07.140 line:80%
This is my dowry prepared by Zigui.

00:37:07.540 --> 00:37:08.410 line:80%
Keep it.

00:37:08.850 --> 00:37:10.740 line:80%
You and Mu Qingyan saw him off.

00:37:11.220 --> 00:37:12.180 line:80%
I have to thank you.

00:37:13.060 --> 00:37:14.890 line:80%
Actually, we came today

00:37:14.890 --> 00:37:15.850 line:80%
to talk

00:37:15.850 --> 00:37:17.370 line:80%
with you.

00:37:17.370 --> 00:37:18.210 line:80%
You want to ask

00:37:19.180 --> 00:37:21.140 line:80%
about Mu Qingyan, right?

00:37:21.140 --> 00:37:22.180 line:80%
Tell me the truth.

00:37:22.700 --> 00:37:23.660 line:80%
Why did you

00:37:23.970 --> 00:37:25.290 line:80%
go with him?

00:37:26.810 --> 00:37:28.410 line:80%
We wanted to find

00:37:28.410 --> 00:37:30.180 line:80%
who truly killed Uncle Chang.

00:37:30.700 --> 00:37:31.580 line:80%
These weeks,

00:37:32.370 --> 00:37:33.210 line:80%
how did he treat you?

00:37:51.450 --> 00:37:52.490 line:80%
He treated me

00:37:54.740 --> 00:37:55.580 line:80%
very well.

00:37:59.290 --> 00:38:00.450 line:80%
And you?

00:38:04.970 --> 00:38:05.810 line:80%
I...

00:38:07.930 --> 00:38:09.370 line:80%
Do you like him?

00:38:18.000 --> 00:38:28.660 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:38:47.420 --> 00:38:51.830 line:80%
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

00:38:52.395 --> 00:38:57.010 line:80%
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

00:38:57.350 --> 00:39:01.915 line:80%
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

00:39:02.440 --> 00:39:06.740 line:80%
♪Free to wander in the world♪

00:39:09.685 --> 00:39:14.385 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:39:14.910 --> 00:39:19.200 line:80%
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

00:39:19.860 --> 00:39:23.890 line:80%
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

00:39:24.205 --> 00:39:29.330 line:80%
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

00:39:29.905 --> 00:39:34.715 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:39:34.930 --> 00:39:39.100 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:39:39.825 --> 00:39:43.760 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:39:44.260 --> 00:39:49.535 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

00:40:12.265 --> 00:40:17.395 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:40:17.760 --> 00:40:22.130 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:40:22.395 --> 00:40:26.525 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:40:26.710 --> 00:40:32.285 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪